    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the school summer holidays to 7 weeks",
        "additional_details": "We believe many students are getting stressed due to too much time in school. We believe extending the summer holiday to seven weeks would be beneficial for students.",
        "background": "We want the Government to extend the school summer holidays to 7 weeks, by requiring schools to close for at least this long over summer. ",
